trigger.expression: {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.CPU1.temp.last()}>75 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.CPU2.temp.last()}>75 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.CPU3.temp.last()}>75 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.CPU4.temp.last()}>75
trigger.name: CPU temperature critical on {HOSTNAME}

trigger.expression: {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.MEMCPU1.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.MEMCPU2.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.MEMCPU3.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.MEMCPU4.temp.last()}>70
trigger.name: DIMM temperature critical on {HOSTNAME}

trigger.expression: {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.PSU1Power.last()}<1 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.PSU2Power.last()}<1 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.PSU3Power.last()}<1 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.PSU4Power.last()}<1
trigger.name: Power supply issue on {HOSTNAME}

trigger.expression: {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.Baseboard1.temp.last()}>60 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX600 S6:ipmi.Baseboard2.temp.last()}>60
trigger.name: System temperature critical on {HOSTNAME}
